								<p>
The Telephone Consumer Protection Act of 1991 was passed by the United States Congress to protect consumers from telephone solicitations, including SMS text messages. 
Don't worry though, Tatango has you covered when complying with the Telephone Consumer Protection Act.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div class="tour-right-left-right">
