							</div>
							<div class="tour-right-left-right">
								<h2>CTIA Compliance</h2>
								<p>
CTIA - The Wireless Association is in charge of monitoring and enforcing short code usage through the CTIA Compliance Monitoring and Enforcement Playbook. 
Don't worry though, Tatango has your back when it comes to CTIA compliance.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
